P_HTM[1]='*Namo tassa bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa*';
P_HTM[2]='*Khuddakanikāye*';
P_HTM[3]='*Itivuttakapāḷi*';
P_HTM[4]='*1. Ekakanipāto*';
P_HTM[5]='*1. Paṭhamavaggo*';
P_HTM[6]='*1. Lobhasuttaṃ*';
P_HTM[7]='*1. Vuttañhetaṃ  bhagavatā, vuttamarahatāti me sutaṃ –*';
P_HTM[8]='*‘‘Ekadhammaṃ, bhikkhave, pajahatha; ahaṃ vo pāṭibhogo anāgāmitāya. Katamaṃ ekadhammaṃ? Lobhaṃ, bhikkhave, ekadhammaṃ pajahatha; ahaṃ vo pāṭibhogo anāgāmitāyā’’ti. Etamatthaṃ bhagavā avoca. Tatthetaṃ iti vuccati –*';
P_HTM[9]='*‘‘Yena  lobhena luddhāse, sattā gacchanti duggatiṃ;*';
P_HTM[10]='*Taṃ lobhaṃ sammadaññāya, pajahanti vipassino;*';
P_HTM[11]='*Pahāya na punāyanti, imaṃ lokaṃ kudācana’’nti.*';
P_HTM[12]='*Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. Paṭhamaṃ.*';
