P_HTM[16]='*‘‘Yena  dosena duṭṭhāse, sattā gacchanti duggatiṃ;*';
P_HTM[17]='*Taṃ dosaṃ sammadaññāya, pajahanti vipassino;*';
P_HTM[18]='*Pahāya na punāyanti, imaṃ lokaṃ kudācana’’nti.*';
