P_HTM[34]='*5. Makkhasuttaṃ*';
P_HTM[35]='*5. Vuttañhetaṃ  bhagavatā, vuttamarahatāti me sutaṃ –*';
P_HTM[36]='*‘‘Ekadhammaṃ, bhikkhave, pajahatha; ahaṃ vo pāṭibhogo anāgāmitāya. Katamaṃ ekadhammaṃ? Makkhaṃ, bhikkhave, ekadhammaṃ pajahatha; ahaṃ vo pāṭibhogo anāgāmitāyā’’ti. Etamatthaṃ bhagavā avoca. Tatthetaṃ iti vuccati –*';
P_HTM[37]='*‘‘Yena makkhena makkhāse *[makkhitāse (syā.)]*, sattā gacchanti duggatiṃ;*';
P_HTM[38]='*Taṃ makkhaṃ sammadaññāya, pajahanti vipassino;*';
P_HTM[39]='*Pahāya na punāyanti, imaṃ lokaṃ kudācana’’nti.*';
