P_HTM[41]='*6. Mānasuttaṃ*';
P_HTM[42]='*6. Vuttañhetaṃ  bhagavatā, vuttamarahatāti me sutaṃ –*';
P_HTM[43]='*‘‘Ekadhammaṃ, bhikkhave, pajahatha; ahaṃ vo pāṭibhogo anāgāmitāya. Katamaṃ ekadhammaṃ? Mānaṃ, bhikkhave, ekadhammaṃ pajahatha; ahaṃ vo pāṭibhogo anāgāmitāyā’’ti. Etamatthaṃ bhagavā avoca. Tatthetaṃ iti vuccati –*';
P_HTM[44]='*‘‘Yena mānena mattāse, sattā gacchanti duggatiṃ;*';
P_HTM[45]='*Taṃ mānaṃ sammadaññāya, pajahanti vipassino;*';
P_HTM[46]='*Pahāya na punāyanti, imaṃ lokaṃ kudācana’’nti.*';
P_HTM[47]='*Ayampi  attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. Chaṭṭhaṃ.*';
P_HTM[48]='*7. Sabbapariññāsuttaṃ*';
P_HTM[49]='*7. Vuttañhetaṃ bhagavatā, vuttamarahatāti me sutaṃ –*';
P_HTM[50]='*‘‘Sabbaṃ, bhikkhave, anabhijānaṃ aparijānaṃ tattha cittaṃ avirājayaṃ appajahaṃ abhabbo dukkhakkhayāya. Sabbañca kho, bhikkhave, abhijānaṃ parijānaṃ  tattha cittaṃ virājayaṃ pajahaṃ bhabbo dukkhakkhayāyā’’ti. Etamatthaṃ bhagavā avoca. Tatthetaṃ iti vuccati –*';
P_HTM[51]='*‘‘Yo  sabbaṃ sabbato ñatvā, sabbatthesu na rajjati;*';
P_HTM[52]='*Sa ve sabbapariññā *[sabbaṃ pariññā (syā. pī.)]* so, sabbadukkhamupaccagā’’ti *[sabbaṃ dukkhaṃ upaccagāti (syā.), sabbadukkhaṃ upaccagāti (pī. aṭṭha.)]*.*';
P_HTM[53]='*Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. Sattamaṃ.*';
P_HTM[54]='*8. Mānapariññāsuttaṃ*';
P_HTM[55]='*8. Vuttañhetaṃ bhagavatā, vuttamarahatāti me sutaṃ –*';
P_HTM[56]='*‘‘Mānaṃ, bhikkhave, anabhijānaṃ aparijānaṃ tattha cittaṃ avirājayaṃ appajahaṃ abhabbo dukkhakkhayāya. Mānañca kho, bhikkhave, abhijānaṃ parijānaṃ tattha cittaṃ virājayaṃ pajahaṃ bhabbo dukkhakkhayāyā’’ti. Etamatthaṃ bhagavā avoca. Tatthetaṃ iti vuccati –*';
P_HTM[57]='*‘‘Mānupetā ayaṃ pajā, mānaganthā bhave ratā;*';
P_HTM[58]='*Mānaṃ aparijānantā, āgantāro punabbhavaṃ.*';
P_HTM[59]='*‘‘Ye  ca mānaṃ pahantvāna, vimuttā mānasaṅkhaye;*';
P_HTM[60]='*Te mānaganthābhibhuno, sabbadukkhamupaccagu’’nti *[sabbadukkhaṃ upaccagunti (pī.), sabbaṃ dukkhaṃ upaccagunti (aṭṭhakathā)]*.*';
P_HTM[61]='*Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. Aṭṭhamaṃ.*';
P_HTM[62]='*9. Lobhapariññāsuttaṃ*';
P_HTM[63]='*9. Vuttañhetaṃ bhagavatā, vuttamarahatāti me sutaṃ –*';
P_HTM[64]='*‘‘Lobhaṃ, bhikkhave, anabhijānaṃ aparijānaṃ tattha cittaṃ avirājayaṃ appajahaṃ abhabbo dukkhakkhayāya. Lobhañca kho, bhikkhave, abhijānaṃ parijānaṃ tattha cittaṃ virājayaṃ pajahaṃ bhabbo dukkhakkhayāyā’’ti. Etamatthaṃ bhagavā avoca. Tatthetaṃ iti vuccati –*';
P_HTM[65]='*‘‘Yena lobhena luddhāse, sattā gacchanti duggatiṃ;*';
P_HTM[66]='*Taṃ lobhaṃ sammadaññāya, pajahanti vipassino;*';
P_HTM[67]='*Pahāya na punāyanti, imaṃ lokaṃ kudācana’’nti.*';
P_HTM[68]='*Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. Navamaṃ.*';
P_HTM[69]='*10. Dosapariññāsuttaṃ*';
P_HTM[70]='*10. Vuttañhetaṃ  bhagavatā, vuttamarahatāti me sutaṃ –*';
P_HTM[71]='*‘‘Dosaṃ, bhikkhave, anabhijānaṃ aparijānaṃ tattha cittaṃ avirājayaṃ appajahaṃ abhabbo dukkhakkhayāya. Dosañca kho, bhikkhave, abhijānaṃ parijānaṃ tattha cittaṃ virājayaṃ pajahaṃ bhabbo dukkhakkhayāyā’’ti. Etamatthaṃ bhagavā avoca. Tatthetaṃ iti vuccati –*';
P_HTM[72]='*‘‘Yena  dosena duṭṭhāse, sattā gacchanti duggatiṃ;*';
P_HTM[73]='*Taṃ dosaṃ sammadaññāya, pajahanti vipassino;*';
P_HTM[74]='*Pahāya na punāyanti, imaṃ lokaṃ kudācana’’nti.*';
P_HTM[75]='*Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. Dasamaṃ.*';
P_HTM[76]='*Paṭhamo vaggo niṭṭhito.*';
P_HTM[77]='*Tassuddānaṃ –*';
P_HTM[78]='*Rāgadosā atha moho, kodhamakkhā  mānaṃ sabbaṃ;*';
P_HTM[79]='*Mānato rāgadosā puna dve, pakāsitā vaggamāhu paṭhamanti.*';
P_HTM[80]='*2. Dutiyavaggo*';
P_HTM[81]='*1. Mohapariññāsuttaṃ*';
P_HTM[82]='*11. Vuttañhetaṃ bhagavatā, vuttamarahatāti me sutaṃ –*';
P_HTM[83]='*‘‘Mohaṃ, bhikkhave, anabhijānaṃ aparijānaṃ tattha cittaṃ avirājayaṃ appajahaṃ abhabbo dukkhakkhayāya. Mohañca kho, bhikkhave, abhijānaṃ parijānaṃ tattha cittaṃ virājayaṃ pajahaṃ bhabbo dukkhakkhayāyā’’ti. Etamatthaṃ bhagavā avoca. Tatthetaṃ iti vuccati –*';
