P_HTM[88]='*2. Kodhapariññāsuttaṃ*';
P_HTM[89]='*12. Vuttañhetaṃ  bhagavatā, vuttamarahatāti me sutaṃ –*';
P_HTM[90]='*‘‘Kodhaṃ, bhikkhave, anabhijānaṃ aparijānaṃ tattha cittaṃ avirājayaṃ appajahaṃ abhabbo dukkhakkhayāya. Kodhañca kho, bhikkhave, abhijānaṃ parijānaṃ tattha cittaṃ virājayaṃ pajahaṃ bhabbo dukkhakkhayāyā’’ti. Etamatthaṃ bhagavā avoca. Tatthetaṃ iti vuccati –*';
